  26,128,Atabnoona bikulli reeAAin ayatan taAAbathoona
  26,129,Watattakhithoona masaniAAa laAAallakum takhludoona
  26,130,Waitha batashtum batashtum jabbareena
  26,131,Faittaqoo Allaha waateeAAooni
